---
import ServicePage from '../layouts/ServicePage.astro';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What is a butt strip wax?",
    answer: "A butt strip wax (also called a butt crack wax) removes hair from the intergluteal cleft (the area between the buttocks). It can be done as a standalone service or added to a Brazilian wax."
  },
  {
    question: "Does butt strip waxing hurt?",
    answer: "While this area can be more sensitive, our experienced estheticians use techniques to minimize discomfort. The process is quick, and most clients find it manageable."
  },
  {
    question: "Should I get a butt strip wax with my Brazilian?",
    answer: "Many clients choose to add a butt strip wax to their Brazilian for complete hair removal from the entire bikini area. This ensures completely smooth results front to back."
  }
];
---

<ServicePage
  title="Butt Strip Wax Scottsdale | Between the Cheeks Waxing"
  description="Professional butt strip waxing in Scottsdale. Remove hair between the buttocks for clean, smooth results. Available as add-on or standalone. Book today!"
  price="$25"
  duration="10-15 min"
  location="scottsdale" currentLocation="scottsdale"
  faqs={faqs}
>

<!-- Hero Image -->
<div class="mb-8">
  <img 
    src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_8c9102d8-fc86-4223-a453-bbb44fc818a2_butt-strip-wax.jpeg"
    alt="Butt strip waxing service at Rejuvenate You in Scottsdale"
    class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover rounded-xl"
  />
</div>

<p class="text-lg mb-6">
  A butt strip wax (also known as between-the-cheeks waxing) removes unwanted hair from the intergluteal cleft, leaving you completely smooth and confident. This service can be added to your Brazilian wax or booked as a standalone treatment.
</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">What is a Butt Strip Wax?</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="mb-4">
      The butt strip targets the area between the buttocks, removing all hair from the intergluteal cleft. This area is often difficult to maintain with shaving and can be a source of self-consciousness.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our professional waxing service ensures thorough, hygienic removal with minimal discomfort.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <img 
      src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_16da6a34-b6ce-4108-ba29-b3efd83e74d6_benefits-of-butt-wax.jpeg"
