    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">1.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Comfortable Positioning</strong> — You'll be positioned comfortably on your side for easy access and your comfort.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">2.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Cleansing</strong> — The area is thoroughly cleansed before waxing.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">3.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Wax Application</strong> — Hard wax is applied to the area for gentle, effective hair removal.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">4.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Removal & Soothing</strong> — Hair is removed quickly and soothing products are applied.
